description: Yummies Drive Up is cruisin’ through town and servin’ up a swell selection of hearty gourmet sandwiches that are the tastiest around. Locals absolutely love their massive eats, like Yummies’ famously luscious Lobster Roll, which brims with succulent lobster meat. So get yo’ tummies over to the ever-so-retro Yummies Drive Up, because when it comes to big flavorful bites at favorably small prices, this is the truck that the foodies of Massachusetts consistently choose.
name: Yummies Drive-Up
